    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "NuScale’s exclusive global strategic partner, ENTRA1 Energy (“ENTRA1”), continues its work with Tennessee Valley Authority (“TVA”) to progress planning for what would be the largest nuclear power deployment program in U.S. history which will utilize NuScale technology",
        "bbox": [
            233,
            188,
            930,
            301
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "In February 2026, shareholders of SN Nuclearelectrica SA agreed to advance the RoPower project in Doicești, Romania to the next phase",
        "bbox": [
            237,
            383,
            920,
            459
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "NuScale and Framatome expanded their longstanding global supply chain partnership across the United States and Europe to support accelerated fuel delivery",
        "bbox": [
            237,
            559,
            932,
            635
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "NuScale maintained its strong liquidity position ending the first quarter of 2026 with \\$1 billion in liquidity and capital resources",
