            362,
            933,
            435
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "ENTRA1 has indicated that they are continuing to progress toward a power purchase agreement with TVA",
        "bbox": [
            450,
            457,
            918,
            529
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "ENTRA1 is positioned to receive investment capital to help supply large-scale baseload power infrastructure under the \\$550 billion U.S.-Japan Framework Agreement",
